1. copy "open_Modelsim.sh" in the simulation directory

2. using terminal go to the simulation directory and give the following command:

source open_ModelSim.sh

3. create work library with:

vlib work

4. modify the "compile.do" file (updating the file paths) and the "run.do" file

5. in modelsim transcirpts give the command:

do compile.do
